<taxonomicName authority="Last, Manjaji-Matsumoto &amp; Pogonoski, 2008" authorityName="Last, Manjaji-Matsumoto &amp; Pogonoski" authorityYear="2008" box="[305,967,404,429]" class="Elasmobranchii" family="Dasyatidae" genus="Maculabatis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Myliobatiformes" pageId="17" pageNumber="362" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="astra">
<emphasis box="[305,405,405,428]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="362">M. astra</emphasis>
(Last, Manjaji-Matsumoto &amp; Pogonoski, 2008)
